cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.SY

This paper proposes a new dropout scheme for deep learning models that enables more robust prediction and uncertainty quantification. The paper also introduces a new semi-implicit VAE model. Given these topics, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
